### Health Check (Verify Server and Service)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wordsearch/health

### Get All Topics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wordsearch/topics

### Get a Specific Topic (e.g., Travel)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wordsearch/topics/travel

### Save Topic Completion (Progress)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/wordsearch/progress
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "testUser",
  "topicId": "Travel",
  "completed": true,
  "timeSpent": "00:05:00"
}


### Get Topic Completion Status for a User and Topic (e.g., testUser and Travel)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wordsearch/progress/testUser/Travel

### Get All Topic Completions for a User (e.g., testUser)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wordsearch/progress/testUser

### Get User Statistics (e.g., for testUser) - Note: Fix the @GetMapping in code if needed to "/users/{userName}/stats"
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wordsearch/users/testUser/stats

### Admin: Create New Topic
POST http://localhost:8080/api/wordsearch/admin/topics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topicId": "travel",
  "title": "Travel",
  "difficulty": "Easy",
  "gridSize": 12,
  "wordCount": 6,
  "words": ["AIRPORT", "CONVENIENT", "DESTINATION", "FOREIGN", "SOUVENIR", "LUGGAGE"]
}

### Admin: Update Topic (e.g., Travel)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/wordsearch/admin/topics/travel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Travel",
  "difficulty": "Hard",
  "gridSize": 12,
  "words": ["NEW", "WORDS"]
}

### Admin: Delete Topic (e.g., NewTopic)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/wordsearch/admin/topics/Travel